title: MisterMusic Show 312 -new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 312 -[2 hours] 192kbps MP3 stereo-



On this episode of The MisterMusic Show, new music from The Bilinda Butchers, Manic Street Preachers, and Gulp.
Plus an alternative rock hit from July 1990 is the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that was written in the cab on the way to the studio, that ended up being the band's biggest hit.

Mixing new indie and alternative music with over 5 decades of hits....the MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard on RockXS Radio.
